Hello Everyone,

I just joined this group, and started ready through the messages last night.
I am not new to EVP research; I have been doing this research and keeping
records for the past 5 years.  I am excited about the method you are all
trying now using EVP Maker and the wav file on the alphabet.  I would also
like to try this, in the past I have used a white noise generator, fan,
water, light harp music, and even tried using the parabolic microphone to
amplify the spirits voice coming through on the computer.

I look forward to sharing any ideas with the group, and hopefully someone
can direct me more on the research you are all trying.  Would like to
contribute to the group in any way I can.  Now off to listen to some of the
evps captured through this methodï¿½:-)

Mercy

--Boundary_(ID_ZX9ccyuGALhv6D83HitrxQ)
